column4: NSLOCTEXT("[A4F8394440FBB5FA44030A8A0716C521]", "9CC8D12C49473273AD8FB3A363FC3AA2", "No, I don\'t want to! I don\'t want to fight!")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4F8394440FBB5FA44030A8A0716C521]", "03C1460147D734251A5AC1BF72CBA12B", "If you don\'t want to fight, then run away.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4F8394440FBB5FA44030A8A0716C521]", "D2B7D1B54D835C118369769897A6A73E", "Oh well, why don\'t you come to our city? Better than hiding out here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4F8394440FBB5FA44030A8A0716C521]", "BA055A5F4B219D5B0DBCD496C58157BA", "We are not going to force you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4F8394440FBB5FA44030A8A0716C521]", "855CDE8F42B998FF6538CCB2B75F975E", "That makes me want to go. Okay, I\'ll go!")
